
Help on: gnome

Gnomes are small cave dwellers. They tend to be nimble
but frail due to their small size. They make up for
their weak physique by being strong of will and stubborn.
Unfortenately, this makes them rather unpleasant company.

               Physical:         Mental:

    Strength:  bad               above average
Constitution:  bad               good
   Dexterity:  good              average
    Charisma:  poor              bad
